displayName: Golden City Dromos, Prince Faction Headquarters 2F

parameters:
Prince Rex: What I want to talk to you about is our
future.
Priestess Sophia: Yes, I am prepared.

Prince Rex: You may have misunderstood something, but I
have no intention of letting go of Alicia or Sophia.

Prince Rex: I should have told you before, but it was love
at first sight, and it still is.

Prince Rex: You, who rescued me at that time, are the
greatest contributor when I become king.

Prince Rex: I won't let anyone complain or take orders from
anyone. I will decide my partner.

Former Imperial Dark Agent Alicia: Looking back now, the
days when I escaped from pursuers with Prince Rex were the
most free and shining moments of my life.

Former Imperial Dark Agent Alicia: I was freed from the
days as a torturer and was able to spend time with the
wonderful Prince Rex.

Young Rex: I was the same. It was when I had the heaviest
responsibility as a prince that my heart was the most
stable.

Young Rex: In front of me is a dignified yet adorable
woman... It was certainly a free and wonderful time for me
too.
Young Rex: How should I express something like that...

Former Imperial Dark Agent Alicia: It's probably our
youth... Those days of youth that came too late for us, that
time.

Former Imperial Dark Agent Alicia: And within our youth, we
fell in love.
Young Rex: That's right, that's why, I...

Former Imperial Dark Agent Alicia: It was a love that
burned me, and it wasn't just love.

Former Imperial Dark Agent Alicia: We were too young for
love to burn out, and too young for love to fully blossom in
such a short time.

Priestess Sophia: Now, I have become 'watashi' to you, and
you have become 'watashi' to me...

Priestess Sophia: You have become a prince from a young
man, and I have become a priestess from a torturer...

Priestess Sophia: And so, the days of your youth as a
prince come to an end, and we have our own missions to
fulfill for each other.

Prince Rex: The innocent time has come to an end... That's
what I want to say.

Priestess Sophia: I will never forget the sun of that day,
the warmth, and you as a young man.

Priestess Sophia: I love you, Prince Rex, so please
remember me and us... and...

Former Imperial Dark Agent Alicia: Please forget about it
someday...

Prince Rex: It was the friends who changed you, both
lovable and wonderful companions...

Prince Rex: I am just a persistent man. When I become king,
I want to hear your answer again.
Prince Rex: Shall we go down, Sophia?
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
